Titolo: Minelvaton Saga: Ragon no Fukkatsu

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: Minelvaton Saga: Ragon no Fukkatsu (ミネルバトンサーガ ラゴンの復活, Minelvaton Saga: Ragon's Revival) is a role playing game published by Taito for the Family Computer. It is the first game in the Minelvaton series, being followed by Silva Saga and ending with Silva Saga II: The Legend of Light and Darkness.
A tribute CD Minelvaton Saga Tribute was published in 2009.